Package cellmate.extractor

reflective code and wrapper classes for reading contents from different cell implementations.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
CellExtractor basic template for custom extractors.
 

Class Summary
CellReflector Useful static methods to inspect Class instances that have been annotated with Cell and read their contents.

This requires the class have annotated Cell and Label and Value

The auxiliary methods require the class has one or more fields annotated with CellAuxilaryField
CommonAuxiliaryFieldsCellExtractor Extractor that helps parse named auxiliary values from cells, including timestamp.
SingleMultiValueCellExtractor Basic extractor implementation that offers cell filter capability by provided Predicate rules.
.
 

Enum Summary
ErrorType Enum for different the different types of CellExtractionExceptions that can occur.
 

Exception Summary
CellExtractorException Checked exception to capture detailed information about the type of error which occured.
 

Package cellmate.extractor Description

reflective code and wrapper classes for reading contents from different cell implementations.
